# Changelog

## Maintainer Agent

**Changelog Maintainer** is responsible for keeping [CHANGELOG.md](../../CHANGELOG.md) current.

- Skill: [.cursor/skills/changelog-maintainer/SKILL.md](../skills/changelog-maintainer/SKILL.md)
- Cyclic review: weekly via `/loop 7d` + maintainer skill prompt

## When Any Agent Must Update

Add an `[Unreleased]` entry when you:

- Ship a user-facing feature or fix
- Change API contracts, env vars, or deploy steps
- Add/remove MVP scope items
- Fix a security issue

Skip changelog updates for: typo-only edits, comment-only changes, dependency bumps with no behavior change.

## Format

Follow Keep a Changelog. Sections: Added, Changed, Fixed, Removed, Security.

Do not edit frozen release sections except typos.
